Last Broadcast Date: Tue 10 Jan 2012
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, the Afghan woman who's opened the country's first bowling alley, the American woman who married into the strange world of clowning and became a clown herself and the British artist who's produced a comic book about the death of her two year old son, as a way of coping with her grief. Show less